{"tid":1667322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得 陳同佳其實好慘 兩頂綠帽 仲要多個便宜仔","createTime":"2019-10-21T11:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T14:59:44.000Z","uid":216555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bcaa61b3e2beda66827420d8bd209dcf42c48fa3","tid":1667322,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:36:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">利中唔主張殺人 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n-女朋友罪狀<br />\n偷食大肚 <br />\n有SP <br />\n夠膽死大緊人地肚用陳同佳辛苦錢去旅行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佳仔帶咗兩頂綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  一個女朋友比緊兩個唔識嘅人玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女朋友每日就係咁樣俾人抽插  35度精液每日咁慢慢流入女朋友陰道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2H9G5GG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2H9G5GG.png&h=e49792a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b881fe47bdbf06adf19bbb8d83e484b8d53c88d0","tid":1667322,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bac6bba79b09b0a3b37fd61e2336268d44f05c4","tid":1667322,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74a7c79b7f4031c64aeb58134ac09d35416ad4f6","tid":1667322,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"860e1defdb690dc9de917301e9e607571f6c1b4e","tid":1667322,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h93TUgu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh93TUgu.gif&h=2b5b378f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被港共正苦壓迫既人先真正慘<br />\n寧化厲鬼<br />\n不作浮塵<br />\n天滅中共<br />\n地毀林鄭<br />\n解散警隊<br />\n刻不容緩"},{"pid":"74b1ee8b4f18d2000e2e993f9745be6c6bf6dda0","tid":1667322,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"0caebaf94c8202380655228fb7e729464fd9c96f","tid":1667322,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:59:44.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}